{"tid":1211464,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"情報封鎖討論","createTime":"2019-06-12T15:49:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T16:06:52.000Z","uid":161059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"27852b8d413fdcd2b08dee1b56512976fde5830e","tid":1211464,"uid":161059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:49:21.000Z","msg":"想問下如果政府已安全為由，封鎖連登（or facebook,ig)有關返佔中示威嘅post,咁我哋會唔會大大失去左情報收集<br />\n嘅能力？<br />\n<br />\n有好多人連今日流會之後應該點做都冇一個共識，如果政府真係封鎖左連登，咁樣好似會大大破壞左我哋嘅組織能力？<br />\n<br />\n因為如果政府真係封鎖左討論區嘅話， 大部份即時緊急訊息都只能透過telegram 大氣電波來傳達，我哋係咪應該做二手準備？（設立多個討論區）<br />\n<br />\n定其實純粹係我智障其實就算封鎖左都沒所謂，香港人自然會識得去邊度示威？又或者其實有更多渠道可以收集情報？如果有請分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7b3c0555d6a12a2fa2345b486cc0a96c25a39e1","tid":1211464,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:50:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />⋯"},{"pid":"32ac08fb45373d3459d99efa90a018a614d31623","tid":1211464,"uid":63119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:57:29.000Z","msg":"Telegram 個巴打被拉左，我都好擔心連仔會有事。<br />\n你知啦連登好多j圖架麻，無得睇會好慘"},{"pid":"ea3a4b43db162d0cdfb437c6810e91b386406973","tid":1211464,"uid":161059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32ac08fb45373d3459d99efa90a018a614d31623","tid":1211464,"uid":63119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:57:29.000Z","msg":"Telegram 個巴打被拉左，我都好擔心連仔會有事。<br />\n你知啦連登好多j圖架麻，無得睇會好慘"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:06:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />生死存亡 仲顧住打j<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}